body_html:
Hi guys,
I implemented some example application using TensorFlow Java API with YOLOv2 as model and Gradle as build and dependency management tool. You can see my example here: https://github.com/szaza/tensorflow-example-java.
There is one more application where I implemented an image recognition web service by using Spring Framework, you can see the source code here: https://github.com/szaza/tensorflow-java-examples-spring.
A live demo is available on the Google Cloud here: http://35.231.120.117:8080/

body:
Hi guys,
I implemented some example application using TensorFlow Java API with YOLOv2 as model and Gradle as build and dependency management tool. You can see my example here: https://github.com/szaza/tensorflow-example-java.
There is one more application where I implemented an image recognition web service by using Spring Framework, you can see the source code here: https://github.com/szaza/tensorflow-java-examples-spring.
A live demo is available on the Google Cloud here: http://35.231.120.117:8080/
